data.description: Just in time for the holidays, this private oasis awaits! Entertain inside or out! Open kitchen-living area with brick, wood burning fireplace and in-ceiling surround sound system. Five Bedrooms, or four with dedicated office space. Granite kitchen counter tops with custom cabinetry including glass inset display cabinet. The master suite is like walking into a spa with tile floor and airstone accent wall. Master bathroom has his and her vanities, separate shower, garden tub and in-ceiling bluetooth speaker! Bamboo flooring in living, ancillary bedrooms, dining and office. All lighting has been upgraded. Finished out shop with double garage door in the front and single in the back. Fully finished with electric and drywall, including 2nd story. The detached garage features a large covered patio that looks on to the beautiful in-ground pool with black-glass pebble finish, silver stamped concrete decking, deck jets and LED lighting. NEW ROOF, HVAC, and HOT WATER HEATER!!!
